
& gunnery-laser
 
 >> Help: Gunnery-Laser (Gunnery Skill)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Used for firing laser weapons (such as Small/Medium/Large Laser/Pulse Laser/
 ERLaser).
 
 To see specifics on laser weapons, type 'help laser-weapons'.
 
 For a detailed look at this skill, see our online documentation:
 docs.btmux.com/index.php/Skills%2C_Stats%2C_Attributes%2C_and_Advantages
 
